item.title: CVE-2020-15165|2024-08-04T13:08:22.249Z -- maxieds -- chameleonminilivedebugger
item.description: Version 1.1.6-free of Chameleon Mini Live Debugger on Google Play Store may have had it's sources or permissions tampered by a malicious actor. The official maintainer of the package is recommending all users upgrade to v1.1.8 as soon as possible. For more information, review the referenced GitHub Security Advisory.
